Pakistan.

551
00:51:55,958 --> 00:51:57,625
Sworn enemies..

552
00:51:58,125 --> 00:52:02,000
Can become great friends too.

553
00:52:02,500 --> 00:52:04,708
Are you here for anything special?

554
00:52:05,208 --> 00:52:07,000
She's interested in the Rubaiyat.

555
00:52:07,500 --> 00:52:09,416
And I am interested in her.

556
00:52:09,916 --> 00:52:11,375
I see.

557
00:52:11,875 --> 00:52:13,291
Two hundred dollars.

558
00:52:13,791 --> 00:52:19,333
Yes this choosen.. two hundred thousand dollars.

559
00:52:19,833 --> 00:52:21,333
Excuse me.

560
00:52:21,833 --> 00:52:24,000
Five thousand dollars.

561
00:52:24,500 --> 00:52:28,000
Thank you very much. so have two fifty thousand dollars.

562
00:52:44,625 --> 00:52:45,166
Hello, prince.

563
00:52:45,666 --> 00:52:49,166
What are you doing here?

564
00:53:09,166 --> 00:53:12,666
Where is Daya Master?

565
00:53:40,750 --> 00:53:42,333
I thought the Tigers were finished.

566
00:53:42,833 --> 00:53:45,875
What are you doing here?

567
00:53:46,375 --> 00:53:48,083
Tell me. - Item no. 242.

568
00:53:48,583 --> 00:53:49,958
Since when did you start reading poetry, Prince?

569
00:53:50,458 --> 00:53:51,208
What is 242?

570
00:53:51,708 --> 00:53:54,958
The next item is lot no. 242.

571
00:53:55,458 --> 00:53:59,500
A collection of love poems from Persian poet Omar Khayyam.

572
00:54:00,000 --> 00:54:03,333
The opening bid for this will be $75,000.

573
00:54:03,833 --> 00:54:05,666
$75,000 from the gentleman at the back.

574
00:54:06,166 --> 00:54:06,791
Thank you very much.

575
00:54:07,291 --> 00:54:10,375
$90,000. $125,000.

576
00:54:10,875 --> 00:54:12,750
$400,000. $450,000.

577
00:54:13,250 --> 00:54:14,250
Come on, prince. Come on.

578
00:54:14,750 --> 00:54:16,208
$500,000, going once.

579
00:54:16,708 --> 00:54:17,833
It's a bomb. - Going twice.

580
00:54:18,333 --> 00:54:19,541
KV series, Russian.

581
00:54:20,041 --> 00:54:21,208
Nuclear bomb?

582
00:54:21,708 --> 00:54:25,500
Sold. Lot no. 242, the Rubaiyat of Omar Khayyam..

583
00:54:26,000 --> 00:54:29,166
.. sold to Mr. David Kazan for half a million dollars.

584
00:54:29,666 --> 00:54:32,500
Excuse me.

585
00:54:33,000 --> 00:54:35,791
It most buy of the sold interit conection..

586
00:54:36,291 --> 00:54:37,958
Where were you, Mr. Khambatta?

587
00:54:38,458 --> 00:54:41,166
Ruby and the Rubaiyat are both gone.

588
00:54:41,666 --> 00:54:45,166
Thank you.

589
00:56:05,875 --> 00:56:08,000
For activation, in those days

590
00:56:08,500 --> 00:56:10,541
.. the command validation of a Russian satellite was required

591
00:56:11,041 --> 00:56:12,791
But we have made changes.

592
00:56:13,291 --> 00:56:14,833
You need to enter a password that's all..

593
00:56:15,333 --> 00:56:16,583
.. that is required for activation.

594
00:56:17,083 --> 00:56:21,708
This Rubaiyat of Omar Khayyam is the detonator.

595
00:56:22,208 --> 00:56:25,708
Don't lose it.

596
00:56:55,583 --> 00:56:58,458
So, my congratulations, Mr. Kazan. - Thank you.

597
00:56:58,958 --> 00:57:02,458
And thank you, Dr. Rana, for your contributions. - Thank you.

598
00:57:07,000 --> 00:57:10,500
What time is flight, Dr. Rana?

599
00:57:21,083 --> 00:57:25,208
Cheers. - Cheers.

600
00:57:25,708 --> 00:57:27,666
Dr. Rana, this is the best champagne in the world.

601
00:57:28,166 --> 00:57:31,666
And you are drinking water.

602
00:57:43,375 --> 00:57:45,041
His job was done.

603
00:57:45,541 --> 00:57:49,041
Can you take care of him?

604
00:58:03,500 --> 00:58:06,041
Freddie Khambatta.

605
00:58:06,541 --> 00:58:08,083
I am Colonel.

606
00:58:08,583 --> 00:58:09,958
Why are you standing here?

607
00:58:10,458 --> 00:58:12,416
Join the party.

608
00:58:12,916 --> 00:58:14,000
Party's over, Colonel.

609
00:58:14,500 --> 00:58:18,000
The party's just begun.

610
00:58:20,375 --> 00:58:23,208
If you see my mother again..

611
00:58:23,708 --> 00:58:25,333
.. then tell her I said Hi.

612
00:58:25,833 --> 00:58:31,625
Whoever he is, get rid of him.

613
00:58:32,125 --> 00:58:35,625
Hello, my dear.

614
00:58:46,125 --> 00:58:47,958
The pipeline goes through this lane..

615
00:58:48,458 --> 00:58:51,250
.. and we have an observation post every 10 kilometers.

616
00:58:51,750 --> 00:58:55,333
Sir, there's a call for you.

617
00:58:55,833 --> 00:58:58,625
Hello.

618
00:58:59,125 --> 00:59:01,750
Hello, Mr. Nawaz.

619
00:59:02,250 --> 00:59:04,625
Hello, Mr. lftekhaar.

620
00:59:05,125 --> 00:59:07,500
I can hear raging fire and roaring rain.

621
00:59:08,000 --> 00:59:08,750
You are in Chaman.

622
00:59:09,250 --> 00:59:10,375
Impressive, Mr. Nawaz.

623
00:59:10,875 --> 00:59:12,208
Even at this age, you still have keen ears.

624
00:59:12,708 --> 00:59:14,791
I can even hear what's happening in Morocco.

625
00:59:15,291 --> 00:59:18,208
I just heard that David Kazan has bought a nuclear bomb.

626
00:59:18,708 --> 00:59:22,000
What? Where did you get this news from?

627
00:59:22,500 --> 00:59:24,791
Mr. Nawaz, you will have to share your source with me.

628
00:59:25,291 --> 00:59:26,666
Because if there's any truth in this..

629
00:59:27,166 --> 00:59:27,666
.. then we'll need to cooperate.

630
00:59:28,166 --> 00:59:29,291
Tell me, General.

631
00:59:29,791 --> 00:59:30,291
Are you involved?

632
00:59:30,791 --> 00:59:31,708
I have no idea.

633
00:59:32,208 --> 00:59:33,083
I didn't know at all.

634
00:59:33,583 --> 00:59:34,416
If I had any clue about this..

635
00:59:34,916 --> 00:59:35,958
.. then I would have called you myself.

636
00:59:36,458 --> 00:59:38,791
Look, Mr. lftekhaar, whatever the problems between us..

637
00:59:39,291 --> 00:59:40,041
.. this cannot be the solution.

638
00:59:40,541 --> 00:59:41,583
Thank you very much.

639
00:59:42,083 --> 00:59:44,250
Give me 12 hours. I will call you back.

640
00:59:44,750 --> 00:59:48,250
Goodbye.

641
00:59:58,541 --> 00:59:59,208
Cancel the inspection.

642
00:59:59,708 --> 01:00:01,166
We will return to Islamabad right now.

643
01:00:01,666 --> 01:00:02,791
Cancel my trip to China.

644
01:00:03,291 --> 01:00:04,000
And call an emergency meeting..

645
01:00:04,500 --> 01:00:05,041
.. of all the section chiefs tomorrow.

646
01:00:05,541 --> 01:00:06,333
Specially section Q, okay.

647
01:00:06,833 --> 01:00:10,333
Fine.

648
01:00:19,291 --> 01:00:22,416
Take lftekhaar sir's convoy to the Turkhum border..

649
01:00:22,916 --> 01:00:26,416
.. and blow it up with a launcher.

650
01:02:05,000 --> 01:02:07,916
I'll keep you posted, sir.

651
01:02:08,416 --> 01:02:09,291
Breaking news.

652
01:02:09,791 --> 01:02:13,291
ISI chief lftekhaar Ahmed killed in a bomb blast.

653
01:02:37,916 --> 01:02:38,708
Is this Zaheer's home?

654
01:02:39,208 --> 01:02:41,666
This is Zaheer's home, but he is on the terrace.

655
01:02:42,166 --> 01:02:45,666
Thank You! - You're welcome

656
01:03:17,833 --> 01:03:19,875
Who are you? - I am Freddie.

657
01:03:20,375 --> 01:03:21,125
Freddie Khambatta. - What?

658
01:03:21,625 --> 01:03:22,250
Yes. I am Freddie.

659
01:03:22,750 --> 01:03:26,250
If you are Freddie then who is he?

660
01:03:30,250 --> 01:03:31,500
So you were telling the truth that day.

661
01:03:32,000 --> 01:03:32,708
You are a RAW agent!

662
01:03:33,208 --> 01:03:34,291
Who is the Colonel?

663
01:03:34,791 --> 01:03:37,000
Where is the bomb? - That's what I came here to find out.

664
01:03:37,500 --> 01:03:38,583
I thought you knew about him.

665
01:03:39,083 --> 01:03:41,791
She's trying to confuse us.

666
01:03:42,291 --> 01:03:43,375
Where is the bomb?

667
01:03:43,875 --> 01:03:46,958
I am on your side.

668
01:03:47,458 --> 01:03:50,416
I work for the British Intelligence.

669
01:03:50,916 --> 01:03:51,666
And you killed that British agent?

670
01:03:52,166 --> 01:03:53,208
I didn't kill Richard.

671
01:03:53,708 --> 01:03:55,458
He was my handler.

672
01:03:55,958 --> 01:03:57,708
I went there to inform him about you.

673
01:03:58,208 --> 01:04:00,458
To show him your face.

674
01:04:00,958 --> 01:04:03,583
You killed 40 people in London.

675
01:04:04,083 --> 01:04:05,833
You were smiling as you got out of the car.

676
01:04:06,333 --> 01:04:09,833
You were smiling.

677
01:04:10,958 --> 01:04:16,875
I was smiling, because I was happy.

678
01:04:17,375 --> 01:04:18,166
It was a beautiful day.

679
01:04:18,666 --> 01:04:21,791
Boss, why are you listening to this nonsense?

680
01:04:22,291 --> 01:04:26,166
I am responsible for the death of those 40 people.

681
01:04:26,666 --> 01:04:29,041
Because my own friends..

682
01:04:29,541 --> 01:04:33,666
.. had planted the bomb in my car.

683
01:04:34,166 --> 01:04:38,416
I was waiting for them.

684
01:04:38,916 --> 01:04:40,916
If I wasn't feeling hungry..

685
01:04:41,416 --> 01:04:44,958
.. and hadn't stepped out..

686
01:04:45,458 --> 01:04:48,958
.. then the blast would have killed me..

687
01:04:51,541 --> 01:04:55,500
When one of the group was caught in Pakistan..

688
01:04:56,000 --> 01:04:59,291
.. then ISI chief lftekhaar Ahmed came to see me.

689
01:04:59,791 --> 01:05:02,000
He was convinced that I am innocent.

690
01:05:02,500 --> 01:05:03,625
He convinced Richard.

691
01:05:04,125 --> 01:05:06,125
They said that they will help me..

692
01:05:06,625 --> 01:05:08,416
.. but I will have to work for them.

693
01:05:08,916 --> 01:05:10,333
They sprung me out of jail..

694
01:05:10,833 --> 01:05:14,250
.. and sent me to Morocco, to Kazan.

695
01:05:14,750 --> 01:05:19,000
Kazan buys drugs from terrorists, and supplies arms.

696
01:05:19,500 --> 01:05:20,666
So you are an ISI agent?

697
01:05:21,166 --> 01:05:22,791
I just report to lftekhaar Sir.

698
01:05:23,291 --> 01:05:24,583
He knows the truth about me.

699
01:05:25,083 --> 01:05:27,625
Last month I intercepted Abu Nazir's phone call from Moscow..

700
01:05:28,125 --> 01:05:31,041
.. that Freddie Khambatta is arriving with $50 million.

701
01:05:31,541 --> 01:05:33,666
I informed Richard, that's why he came here personally.

702
01:05:34,166 --> 01:05:35,666
Can you prove this?

703
01:05:36,166 --> 01:05:37,583
Talk to lftekhaar sir.

704
01:05:38,083 --> 01:05:39,000
He knows me.

705
01:05:39,500 --> 01:05:43,000
lftekhaar Ahmed is dead.

706
01:05:44,375 --> 01:05:46,625
He's dead?

707
01:05:47,125 --> 01:05:48,958
And Richard too.

708
01:05:49,458 --> 01:05:52,541
Now there's no one left to prove your story. And you..

709
01:05:53,041 --> 01:05:56,541
Zahir.

710
01:06:04,500 --> 01:06:05,375
He's one of them.

711
01:06:05,875 --> 01:06:07,333
Now he knows about you.

712
01:06:07,833 --> 01:06:11,333
Shoot him.

713
01:06:16,041 --> 01:06:17,583
No.

714
01:06:18,083 --> 01:06:19,750
I cannot kill anyone.

715
01:06:20,250 --> 01:06:22,291
Not even him.

716
01:06:22,791 --> 01:06:24,500
I don't know where the bomb is.

717
01:06:25,000 --> 01:06:26,791
But the Rubaiyat is the trigger.

718
01:06:27,291 --> 01:06:29,000
The bomb is useless without Rubaiyat.

719
01:06:29,500 --> 01:06:31,500
And right now Rubaiyat is in Kazan's safe.

720
01:06:32,000 --> 01:06:33,416
If you believe me then let me go.

721
01:06:33,916 --> 01:06:34,833
I know the combination of that safe.

722
01:06:35,333 --> 01:06:35,916
Otherwise go yourself.

723
01:06:36,416 --> 01:06:39,916
But for God's sake get that Rubaiyat out of there.

724
01:06:42,541 --> 01:06:43,166
Let's go.

725
01:06:43,666 --> 01:06:47,166
Come on.

726
01:06:59,583 --> 01:07:00,541
20 minutes.

727
01:07:01,041 --> 01:07:04,541
Good luck, Iram.

728
01:07:17,000 --> 01:07:19,333
She was lying.

729
01:07:19,833 --> 01:07:20,875
You believed her?

730
01:07:21,375 --> 01:07:24,875
She was telling the truth.

731
01:08:01,875 --> 01:08:04,416
I have the Rubaiyat and the location of the bomb as well.

732
01:08:04,916 --> 01:08:08,416
Meet me at Golden Farah restaurant, in 20 minutes.

733
01:08:47,958 --> 01:08:51,458
Get lost.

734
01:09:05,833 --> 01:09:09,583
"My friends deserted me."

735
01:09:10,083 --> 01:09:14,416
"My love deserted me."

736
01:09:14,916 --> 01:09:18,208
"Life's so.."

737
01:09:18,708 --> 01:09:19,708
Indian?

738
01:09:20,208 --> 01:09:23,708
Oh, good. Number one.

739
01:10:50,166 --> 01:10:53,666
Goodbye to Morocco.

740
01:11:23,250 --> 01:11:24,583
Indian? - Yes.

741
01:11:25,083 --> 01:11:25,541
I am Suresh Krishna.

742
