That's funny.. - My name is also Suresh Krishna.

743
01:11:29,833 --> 01:11:31,333
By the way, I work for the United Nations.

744
01:11:31,833 --> 01:11:34,791
Deputy Health Commissioner for Africa.

745
01:11:35,291 --> 01:11:36,083
