746
01:11:36,583 --> 01:11:40,083
I am the Deputy Health Commissioner for Africa.

747
01:12:16,000 --> 01:12:18,750
We need to ask you some questions, Mr. Shastri.

748
01:12:19,250 --> 01:12:21,416
How are you feeling?

749
01:12:21,916 --> 01:12:25,416
I am hungry.

750
01:12:37,291 --> 01:12:39,416
We found Mr. Kazan's address in your pocket.

751
01:12:39,916 --> 01:12:41,958
He's dead. His house has been burgled.

752
01:12:42,458 --> 01:12:44,625
How do you know him? - I mean him in an auction.

753
01:12:45,125 --> 01:12:48,625
Don't disturb the patient please.

754
01:12:51,666 --> 01:12:54,000
I need to examine the patient Officers.

755
01:12:54,500 --> 01:12:58,000
I will see you in some time.

756
01:13:01,791 --> 01:13:04,500
Good morning. - Good morning, Doctor.

757
01:13:05,000 --> 01:13:07,041
Three bullets and you're still alive.

758
01:13:07,541 --> 01:13:10,083
You must be really lucky.

759
01:13:10,583 --> 01:13:12,333
Do you believe in luck?

760
01:13:12,833 --> 01:13:17,708
If I believed in luck I'd be dead a long time ago, Doctor.

761
01:13:18,208 --> 01:13:21,708
I see.

762
01:13:27,041 --> 01:13:30,541
Do you believe in luck, doctor?

763
01:13:39,291 --> 01:13:41,250
Where is she?

764
01:13:41,750 --> 01:13:43,000
Where is she?

765
01:13:43,500 --> 01:13:44,708
Where is she? - Riga.

766
01:13:45,208 --> 01:13:48,708
Riga.

767
01:13:59,750 --> 01:14:03,250
Do you know where they are?

768
01:14:37,250 --> 01:14:40,750
Look at that man closely.

769
01:14:52,708 --> 01:14:53,708
Anton Brega.

770
01:14:54,208 --> 01:14:56,041
Considers himself a Casanova.

771
01:14:56,541 --> 01:14:58,541
He is an alcoholic.. and a womanizer

772
01:14:59,041 --> 01:15:00,625
He has one more bad habit.

773
01:15:01,125 --> 01:15:02,791
He's honest.

774
01:15:03,291 --> 01:15:04,833
He's the Airport Security chief.

775
01:15:05,333 --> 01:15:08,833
There's a pass card in his wallet which I want.

776
01:15:09,333 --> 01:15:11,250
We'll be done by 2 o'clock tomorrow afternoon.

777
01:15:11,750 --> 01:15:14,208
Until then you will have to keep him out of the airport.

778
01:15:14,708 --> 01:15:20,958
So.. you have to spend the night with him.

779
01:15:21,458 --> 01:15:23,416
