780
01:15:23,916 --> 01:15:27,416
Bloody reptile!

781
01:15:29,375 --> 01:15:30,375
I just want to die.

782
01:15:30,875 --> 01:15:34,375
No, actually, I just want to get drunk.

783
01:15:39,166 --> 01:15:41,250
Sorry. - No, that's okay. That's fine.

784
01:15:41,750 --> 01:15:42,791
Give me another one.

785
01:15:43,291 --> 01:15:44,583
What do you want? Just get lost.

786
01:15:45,083 --> 01:15:47,833
Okay. Sir, please.

787
01:15:48,333 --> 01:15:51,833
Thank you.

788
01:15:53,083 --> 01:15:56,583
Anton Brega. - Josie.

789
01:16:10,333 --> 01:16:13,833
I told you to get lost.

790
01:17:12,291 --> 01:17:16,000
We just got out of the third casino.

791
01:17:16,500 --> 01:17:17,958
He has won around three-four lakhs.

792
01:17:18,458 --> 01:17:20,250
He says I am lucky for him.

793
01:17:20,750 --> 01:17:22,208
Now he wants to take me home.

794
01:17:22,708 --> 01:17:23,333
Two more hours.

795
01:17:23,833 --> 01:17:24,625
Our job will be done.

796
01:17:25,125 --> 01:17:27,083
Take him to Hotel Riga. 405.

797
01:17:27,583 --> 01:17:28,458
There's a room booked in the name of Josie.

798
01:17:28,958 --> 01:17:32,208
Yeah, 405. - Darling, I've got some special champagne for you.

799
01:17:32,708 --> 01:17:36,208
That's for you. Look at it.

800
01:17:44,583 --> 01:17:48,083
Goodbye.

801
01:17:59,750 --> 01:18:00,458
Hello, sir.

802
01:18:00,958 --> 01:18:03,000
Welcome to Riga. Mr. Nawaz called from Delhi.

803
01:18:03,500 --> 01:18:07,000
This packet is for you.

804
01:18:08,625 --> 01:18:13,041
Any news about those two?

