01:18:59,250 --> 01:19:00,750
Hello.

812
01:19:01,250 --> 01:19:04,750
Excuse me.

813
01:19:08,583 --> 01:19:09,375
Yes.

814
01:19:09,875 --> 01:19:11,291
That Brega is after me.

815
01:19:11,791 --> 01:19:12,791
He's about to jump on me.

816
01:19:13,291 --> 01:19:14,083
Relax.

817
01:19:14,583 --> 01:19:15,625
Open the mini bar.

818
01:19:16,125 --> 01:19:17,166
There's a chocolate box inside.

819
01:19:17,666 --> 01:19:18,583
Feed him some of those chocolates.

